metadata.name: Legends
metadata.description:
The Exploited headlined Scotland Calling 2019 at the O2 Academy in Glasgow.

In this shot we see singer Wattie joined onstage by Charlie Harper of the UK Subs for a brilliant version of 'Troops of Tomorrow'.

Punk rock legends in action!

The first owner of this NFT can claim a professionally created A4 1/1 print.
